+false command
+=============
+
+Synopsis
+--------
+
+::
+
+    false
+
+Description
+-----------
+
+The false command sets the return value $? to 1 (false).
+
+Example
+-------
+
+::
+
+    => false; echo $?
+    1
+    =>
+
+Configuration
+-------------
+
+The false command is only available if CONFIG_HUSH_PARSER=y.
